{"tid":1530014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[831事件重組] 逐分鐘重組當晚 2230-2258 發生既事","createTime":"2019-09-02T00:27:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T01:14:22.000Z","uid":20414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"526479497f00aa20d95414a58be6514c5509b578","tid":1530014,"uid":20414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T00:27:12.000Z","msg":"831 事件還原<br />\n<br />\n22:30 示威者到達旺角 Protestors Arrived MK<br />\n<br />\n22:32 防暴於彌敦道出動 Riot Squad out on Nathan Road<br />\n<br />\n22:36 示威者打破旺角站玻璃 Protestor brake glass in station<br />\n<br />\n22:38 防暴出現於站內 Riot Squad in station (outside pay area)<br />\n<br />\n22:39 示威者登上往觀塘列車 Protestors boarded the train towards KT<br />\n<br />\n22:40 往觀塘列車開出 Train to KT doors shut<br />\n<br />\n22:42 列車到達太子, 發生打鬥 Train arrived PE and started fighting<br />\n<br />\n22:50 打鬥結束, 示威者撤離 Fight ended and protestors leaving<br />\n<br />\n三四號月台列車一直開門  Note: Both train on Platform 3 and 4 left doors open<br />\n<br />\n緊急廣播呼籲乘客撤離 Evacuation siren heard and asked all people to leave<br />\n<br />\n22:50 大量警員登上往太子專列 Police boarded the train from MK (didn&rsquo;t leave until 11)<br />\n<br />\n22:55 防暴出動追捕示威者 Raptors entered PE station and chasing protestors<br />\n <br />\nLink 1 starting time is 14:58 HKT <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/433275987287272/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F433275987287272%2F&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FRmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=9752f684\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/433275987287272/</a> <br />\n <br />\nLink 2 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2357551941030317\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2357551941030317&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FRmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=e85281f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2357551941030317</a>"},{"pid":"e42918315c237db968fdc90659074e23